02:56.440 --> 02:58.237
Diane and Alicia,

02:58.270 --> 03:02.206
I have a favor to
ask of you both.

03:02.250 --> 03:03.478
Please...

03:04.980 --> 03:06.516
...if you could...

03:06.550 --> 03:09.519
go see my mom.

03:11.520 --> 03:14.455
