03:14.490 --> 03:16.924
and I was a disappointment.

03:20.930 --> 03:22.659
To the parents

03:22.700 --> 03:26.238
of Miss Henning and Miss Gore,

03:26.270 --> 03:27.532
I am sorry

03:27.570 --> 03:30.004
