to your daughters,

03:30.040 --> 03:32.372
but I did not do this.

03:32.410 --> 03:34.708
And I wish...

03:34.740 --> 03:37.800
I wish I could say
what was happening

03:37.850 --> 03:39.545
(crowd gasps)
here tonight was just,

03:39.580 --> 03:41.878
because that might
bring you some...

03:41.920 --> 03:44.388
because that might make...

03:45.850 --> 03:49.525
(urgent chattering)

