we'd find much there.

06:17.640 --> 06:19.039
Okay, so we'll break up
into groups.

06:19.070 --> 06:21.573
Tonya, you work the team
on witnesses and testimony.

06:21.610 --> 06:22.747
Carey, the forensics.
Robyn, the background

06:22.780 --> 06:23.769
of the experts.

06:23.810 --> 06:26.540
(garbled transmission)

06:27.720 --> 06:29.745
Thanks, Monica.

06:29.790 --> 06:31.439
Good point.

06:31.490 --> 06:33.549
Am I really needed here
or can I go?

06:33.590 --> 06:34.557
We have 48 hours.

06:34.590 --> 06:36.649
Let's make them c_ount.
Cary, hold on a minute.

06:36.690 --> 06:37.588
Uh, me?

06:37.630 --> 06:38.779
No, Cary-Cary.

06:38.830 --> 06:41.025
Diane, that's not enough time,
is it?

06:41.060 --> 06:43.426
To get a subpoena on the hair
and test it, no.

06:43.470 --> 06:45.028
Okay, you work
your evidentiary track,

06:45.070 --> 06:46.128
