to retest the hair.

06:56.750 --> 06:57.978
Yes?
Someone already retested it

06:58.010 --> 07:00.478
in the prosecutor's office
six years ago.

07:00.520 --> 07:02.010
Right, for an appeal.

07:02.050 --> 07:03.688
No, not in the office
in Indiana,

07:03.720 --> 07:04.948
the one here in Chicago.

07:04.990 --> 07:06.810
Someone tested it here.

07:06.860 --> 07:09.488
Why?

07:09.530 --> 07:10.986
Your dad knows Barry Scheck?

07:11.030 --> 07:13.919
Yeah, he did. Why?

07:13.960 --> 07:15.598
He's in federal court
on an Eighth Amendment

07:15.630 --> 07:17.461
class action right now.

07:17.500 --> 07:18.922
Call him.

07:18.970 --> 07:20.562
Hey, Cary, what's up?

07:20.600 --> 07:22.704
Barry... Mr. Scheck,

07:22.740 --> 07:25.959
we need some help on the
Eddie Alan Fornum appeal.

07:26.010 --> 07:28.069
Oh, I heard his execution
was delayed.

07:28.110 --> 07:29.179
What do you need?

07:29.210 --> 07:30.700
