07:39.760 --> 07:41.751
Hey, I'm glad you're
coming with us.

07:43.160 --> 07:45.822
Oh, hey, uh, Cary
told me the good news.

07:45.860 --> 07:47.623
Can I tell the clients?
What?

07:47.660 --> 07:49.196
The governor's wife is
joining our new firm.

07:49.230 --> 07:50.527
