07:50.570 --> 07:52.629
No, please don't.

07:52.670 --> 07:55.559
Well, that's not what I said.

08:03.250 --> 08:05.502
(elevator bell dings)

08:07.550 --> 08:10.041
Get rid of those,
and let's talk.

08:13.020 --> 08:15.887
Get out of my way!

08:17.890 --> 08:19.551
Here's what I need.

08:19.600 --> 08:21.750
All the phone numbers called
by the fourth-year associates

08:21.800 --> 08:24.166
