are intending to leave

08:27.300 --> 08:29.768
and take some
of our clients with them.

08:29.810 --> 08:31.630
Why do you think that?

08:31.670 --> 08:33.171
Because I'm psychic.

08:33.210 --> 08:34.700
Well, I can't legally access
their calls.

08:34.740 --> 08:36.207
They're using
the company cell phones.

08:36.240 --> 08:37.946
