I can do this, not today.

09:06.740 --> 09:08.207
Okay, Sunday at noon?

09:08.240 --> 09:09.400
At 7:00. What is it again?

09:09.440 --> 09:11.670
It's the basic ethics talk _
for the governor-elect's family.

09:11.710 --> 09:13.575
