if that's all right.

09:49.790 --> 09:50.939
That is all right. Thank you.

09:50.990 --> 09:52.116
I'll see you then.

10:01.260 --> 10:02.727
Yeah, that sounds
about right.

10:02.770 --> 10:04.260
