raising a red flag.

10:05.930 --> 10:07.136
What are we discussing here?

10:07.170 --> 10:09.092
Eli, you've met Marilyn?

10:09.140 --> 10:10.334
Just a few seconds ago
in your office.

10:10.370 --> 10:12.873
