a conflict of interest.

10:23.320 --> 10:24.412
Because I ran
the search committee?

10:24.450 --> 10:26.111
Yes.

10:26.150 --> 10:28.152
Again, I'm not here to
say you can't hire him.

10:28.190 --> 10:29.828
