ethically compromised.

10:32.330 --> 10:33.991
Okay, we'll look into it.
Thanks.

10:34.030 --> 10:35.122
Okay.

10:35.160 --> 10:36.252
Thank you, Marilyn.

10:40.100 --> 10:41.965
