11:29.480 --> 11:31.243
CARY:
All right, I got it.

11:38.030 --> 11:38.883
ASA Pine.

11:38.930 --> 11:40.921
Ms. Lockhart.

11:40.960 --> 11:41.927
Hello.

11:41.960 --> 11:42.892
